<!-- PILLARS -->
<section class="section alt"><div class="wrap">
  <h2 class="sec-h rv">Hand off the big stuff <em>and come back to it done.</em></h2>
  <p class="sec-sub rv">It splits big jobs across specialist subagents and runs them around the clock. <b>You close the laptop; it keeps going.</b></p>
  <div class="pillars rv">
    <div class="pillar"><div class="nm">Stop repeating yourself</div><div class="d"><b>The Vault</b>: it remembers your people, projects, and decisions, across restarts and machines.</div></div>
    <div class="pillar"><div class="nm">Skip the setup</div><div class="d"><b>Awareness</b>: it already sees your screen, so it has context before you finish the sentence.</div></div>
    <div class="pillar"><div class="nm">Delegate the whole job</div><div class="d"><b>Orchestration</b>: it spawns subagents and runs them 24/7, on an authority model you control.</div></div>
  </div>
</div></section>

